The Solution: Decentralized Truth Infrastructure

indelible.Blob creates an immutable verification layer for digital media by capturing provenance data at the source and storing it in a decentralized, cryptographically verifiable format.

Core Innovation

Capture → Verify → Store → Prove

1.
Capture with Context

•
High-accuracy GPS (1-3m, with RTK support for sub-cm )

•
Timestamp at moment of capture

•
Device metadata and sensor data

•
Environmental context (future: weather, lighting, accelerometer)

1.
Decentralized Storage (Walrus)

•
Immutable blob storage

•
No single point of failure

•
Censorship-resistant

•
Permanent availability

1.
Blockchain Verification (Sui)

•
Content hash recorded on-chain

•
Provenance data immutably linked

•
Transparent verification

•
Cryptographic proof of authenticity

1.
Verifiable Provenance

•
Complete chain of custody

•
GPS-verified location

•
Timestamp verification

•
Creator attribution




Current MVP: Functional Prototype

What Works Today

✅ Mobile Capture System (React Native/Expo)

•
Photo and video capture

•
Real-time GPS tracking (1-3m accuracy)

•
Session-based organization

•
Intuitive UI for field use

✅ Walrus Integration

•
Automatic upload to Walrus testnet

•
Blob ID retrieval and storage

•
Public URL generation

•
Status tracking (uploading → verified)

✅ Sui Blockchain Recording

•
Content hash generation (SHA-256)

•
Transaction recording (currently simulated)

•
Immutable verification records

•
Object ID tracking

✅ Verification Interface

•
Library view with session management

•
Blockchain data display

•
GPS metadata visualization

•
Status badges and verification indicators

