Why indelible.Blob Will Win

1. First-Mover Advantage

We're building the infrastructure before the crisis fully manifests. By the time deepfakes are ubiquitous, indelible.Blob will be the established standard.

2. Network Effects

Every verified capture increases the value of the platform. Every media organization that adopts it increases pressure on others to follow.

3. Decentralization as Moat

Centralized solutions can be compromised, censored, or shut down. Decentralized verification is permanent and unstoppable.

4. Multi-Industry Applicability

Not just media—legal, insurance, scientific, creative and A.E.C. The same verification infrastructure serves multiple high-value markets.

5. Technology Convergence

Walrus (storage) + Sui (verification) + Seal (privacy) + Nautilus (compute) = Complete decentralized truth infrastructure.




